# R session

library(pipeR)
library(data.table)
library(jiebaR)
library(tm)
library(tmcn)
library(SnowballC)
library(wordcloud)
old_wd <- getwd()

# US presidents ------------------------
setwd("usP")
removal <- content_transformer(function(x, pattern) gsub(pattern, " ", x)) 

# Setup corpus
us.txt <- list.files(pattern = "\\.txt$")
us <- data.table(
    president = regmatches(us.txt, regexpr("[A-Za-z]+", us.txt)),
    time = as.integer(regmatches(us.txt, regexpr("\\d+", us.txt))),
    corpus = sapply(us.txt, function(X) readChar(X, file.info(X)$size))
)

usTable <- table(us$president)
for (i in names(usTable))
    if (usTable[i] > 1) {
        name <- which(i == us$president)
        for (j in name[1:(length(name) - 1)])
            try(if (us$president[j + 1] != i && us$president[j - 1] != i)
                    us$president[j] <- paste0(i, "OLD"))
    }

us.corpus <- Corpus(VectorSource(us[, paste(.(corpus)), by = president]$V1)) %>>%
             tm_map(removal, "\n|\\\\n|\r") %>>%
             tm_map(removePunctuation) %>>%
             tm_map(removeWords, stopwords("english")) %>>%
             tm_map(content_transformer(tolower)) %>>%
             tm_map(stemDocument)

# Term document matrix
us.tdm <- as.matrix(TermDocumentMatrix(us.corpus))
colnames(us.tdm) <- us[, unique(president)]
us.tdm.sort <- apply(us.tdm, 2, function(x) names(sort(x, decreasing = TRUE)))
head(us.tdm.sort, 20)

# Words frequency and plots
wordFreq <- sort(rowSums(us.tdm), decreasing = TRUE)

mp <- barplot(
    wordFreq[1:50], axisnames = FALSE, col = heat.colors(50), 
    main = "Words Frequency of US Presidents"
)
mtext("from 1789 to 2013")
text(mp, par('usr')[3], names(wordFreq[1:50]), c(1.1, 1.1), srt = 45, xpd = TRUE)

wordcloud(
    names(wordFreq[1:200]), wordFreq[1:200], scale = c(6, .2), 
    random.color= TRUE, colors = brewer.pal(8, "Dark2")
)

# Set difference between presidents

us.tdm.diff <- us.tdm[rowSums(us.tdm != 0) == 1, ]
us.tdm.diff.sort <- apply(us.tdm.diff, 2, function(x) names(sort(x, decreasing = TRUE)))

# TW presidents -----------------------
setwd("twP")

# Setup corpus
tw.txt <- list.files(pattern = "\\.txt$", recursive = TRUE, full.names = TRUE)

mixworker <- worker()
tw <- sapply(tw.txt, function(X) mixworker <= readChar(X, file.info(X)$size)) %>>%
      sapply(function(X) paste(X, collapse = " ")) %>>% 
      gsub(pattern = "", replacement = "", x = .)

# Add metadata
regmatches(tw.txt, regexpr("\\./\\S+/", tw.txt)) <- ""
tw <- data.table(
    president = regmatches(tw.txt, regexpr("^[A-Z]{3}", tw.txt)),
    time = as.integer(regmatches(tw.txt, regexpr("\\d+", tw.txt))),
    corpus = tw
)

twTable <- table(tw$president)

tw.corpus <- Corpus(VectorSource(tw[, paste(.(corpus)), by = president]$V1)) %>>%
             tm_map(removal, "\n|\\\\n|\r") %>>%
             tm_map(removePunctuation) %>>%
             tm_map(removeWords, toTrad(stopwordsCN()))


# Term document matrix
tw.tdm <- as.matrix(TermDocumentMatrix(tw.corpus, list(wordLengths = c(2, Inf))))
colnames(tw.tdm) <- tw[, unique(president)]
tw.tdm.sort <- apply(tw.tdm, 2, function(x) names(sort(x, decreasing = TRUE)))
head(tw.tdm.sort, 25)

# Words frequency and plots
wordFreq <- sort(rowSums(tw.tdm), decreasing = TRUE)

mp <- barplot(
    wordFreq[1:50], axisnames = FALSE, col = heat.colors(50), 
    main = "Words Frequency of TW Presidents"
)
mtext("from 1955 to 2014")
text(mp, par('usr')[3], names(wordFreq[1:50]), c(1.1, 1.1), srt = 45, xpd = TRUE)

wordcloud(
    names(wordFreq[1:200]), wordFreq[1:200], scale = c(6, .5), rot.per = .2,
    random.order = FALSE, random.color = TRUE, colors = brewer.pal(8, "Dark2")
)

# Set difference between presidents
